      "bullets": [
        "Google’s AI data center expansion drove a 48% emission increase since 2019, jeopardizing its 2030 net-zero carbon goals.",
        "Replacing standard search indexing with LLMs like Gemini increases energy consumption per query by an estimated 10x.",
        "Practitioners must prioritize model efficiency, distillation, and specialized hardware like TPU v5p to mitigate unsustainable energy demands."
      ]
